N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4025.4 - Disqualification-ownership

State Regulations

No horse is qualified to be entered or run that is
wholly or partly the property of or leased to or from, or in any way under the
care of superintendence of, a person who is required to be licensed but is
unlicensed, disqualified or ineligible, as provided in this

Subchapter. Notes
